---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'
---

<PageLayout title='Clientes' info={{ slug: '/clientes', hideComment: true }}>
  <section class="clientes-lynx">
    <h1>Nuestros Clientes, Nuestra Mejor Referencia</h1>
    <p class="clientes-subtitle">
      Más de 70 empresas líderes confían en LYNX para transformar y potenciar su gestión.
    </p>
    <p class="clientes-story">
      En LYNX, cada cliente es una historia de éxito. Nos enorgullece acompañar a empresas de todos los tamaños y sectores en su camino hacia la transformación digital. Estas organizaciones han confiado en nuestra tecnología para optimizar sus procesos, innovar y crecer. ¡Conócelas!
    </p>
    <div class="clientes-mosaico">
      {["Santa Monica","Colombian Harmony","Condor Andino","Flowers Party","Bloems","Candelaria Flowers","Magenta Farms","Natural Blooms","San Francisco Garden","Quirama","Jordan Farms","American Flowers","Zion Flowers","Cultivo Las Nubes","Dos Palmas","Florandina","Sunset Valley","Aromas Farms","Hydraflora","Remolinos","Cultiflora","Vanity Farms","Sunshine Flowers","Hydranflowers","Agrirainbow","Antioqueña de Flores","Azulina Farms","Blackriver","Cultivos La Ceja","Expo Flores Capirito","Flores y Follajes de Antioquia","Floresta Flowers","Flores Guadalupe","Horizonte Farms","Insuflores","J&P Flowers","Lord and Flowers","Novamundi","Cultivos Olivares","Ornamentales de Colombia","Princess Farms","Agencia de Inversiones Prospe","Royal Garden","S&J Flowers","Flores San Jeronimo","Surandina de Flores","Varaga Farms","Florco","Latin Flowers","Flores del Este","Express Farms","Novelty Farms","BlueMountaing","Aristi Farms","Beuth Sierra","Celebrity Flowers","Florantioquia","Greenex","Flores Isabelita","Marcapasos","Susan Farms","Pintek","Santini","Garden Flowers","Cosmo Flowers","Cultivos Sayonara","Almer Flowers","Eshkol Premium","Flores Tropicales","Cultivos El Laurel","Malibu Flowers","Arvi Farms","Floretta","Sky Flowers"].map(cliente => (
        <span class="cliente-nombre">{cliente}</span>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="clientes-cta">
      ¿Quieres ser parte de esta comunidad de empresas exitosas?
      <a href="/contacto" class="clientes-boton">Contáctanos</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .clientes-lynx {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa 0%, #fce4ec 100%);
    }
    .clientes-lynx h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #1a237e;
    }
    .clientes-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #3949ab;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .clientes-story {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .clientes-mosaico {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .cliente-nombre {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1976d2;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.08);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      cursor: default;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .cliente-nombre:hover {
      transform: scale(1.08);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.15);
      background: #e3f2fd;
    }
    .clientes-cta {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .clientes-boton {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
      background: #1976d2;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .clientes-boton:hover {
      background: #0d47a1;
    }
  </style>
</PageLayout>
